  "description": "Adds more zombie variations, compatible with Fresh Animations",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: 72px;\"><strong>IMPORTANT! This project will be refactored to More Mob Variations + Fresh Animations, which will include more mob variations besides the zombie</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/3f9f1853338062b065a48609fd0a8b6793ae9422.png\" alt=\"Title\" width=\"900\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">More Zombie Variations + Fresh Animations is an addon for Fresh Animations, and adds new zombie variations.</p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/894c725751d8de9206c7d10a4dc57479e1e91906.png\" alt=\"Fresh Animations Recommended\" width=\"900\" height=\"50\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This pack makes use of another resourcepack called Fresh Animations to add new animations.<br /><strong>This pack will work as a normal resourcepack without Fresh Animations, but potential malfunctions or bugs can appear.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>GET FRESH ANIMATIONS</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/fresh-animations\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img style=\"float: center; margin-right: 10px;\" src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://styles.redditmedia.com/t5_3errm/styles/communityIcon_y1a4gbuv5fea1.png&amp;n=-1\" alt=\"CurseForge\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" /></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/fresh-animations\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img style=\"float: center;\" src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/67560307?s=200&amp;v=4&amp;n=-1\" alt=\"Modrinth\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" /> </a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"included-textures\">Included textures</h2>\n<h3 id=\"build-100\">Build 1.0.0</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Steve</li>\n<li>Noor</li>\n<li>Sunny</li>\n<li>Ari</li>\n<li>Zuri</li>\n<li>Makena</li>\n<li>Kai</li>\n<li>Efe</li>\n</ul>",
